### Planning Cascade

```
STRATEGIC (12 years / 624 weeks)
    └── Budget, max resources, compliance goals
        │
        ├── TACTICAL (Annual → Quarterly)
        │   └── Which trains get D-Overhaul this year
        │       Distribute C-Checks across quarters
        │       │
        │       ├── OPERATIONAL (Monthly → Weekly)
        │       │   └── Allocate B-Checks and A-Checks
        │       │       Adjust based on actual mileage
        │       │       │
        │       │       └── DAILY
        │       │           └── Execute: which trains enter today
        │       │               Rebalance if needed
```

### What Makes It "Wow"

1. **Animated trains** on lines showing operational fleet
2. **Depot with tracks** showing maintenance capacity usage
3. **Planning levels** user can zoom in/out (12yr → day)
4. **Real-time resources** panel
5. **Color-coded maintenance types** (A=blue, B=green, C=yellow, D=red)
6. **Click to drill down** from year to week to day

